	(43,110,1,'End client decided to put project on hold. Reply from Milan based Sudler CFO below:<br><br>--------<br><br>Just off a call with the Client.<br>They’ve had internal discussions and they have decided, also in relation to their very little familiarity with the Veeva platform still being at an implementation phase, to put on hold the programming and delivery of the Symbicort e-detailing. They decided not to use it for their cycle meeting.<br>I apologize for the time that you have dedicated to this and very much appreciate your professional approach.<br>I kindly ask Yannick to keep in touch with you in view of involving you on other projects. We are current expanding the list of preferred vendors in the digital area, particularly for international clients  and would very much like to put in place an MSa with you.<br> <br>Thanks again and we’ll get in touch shortly.<br>Lia','2014-08-11 13:04:13','2014-08-11 13:04:13'),
